7
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:19,900
This was Hong Kong on Sunday.

8
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:21,660
Not a good day for commuters.

9
00:00:21,660 --> 00:00:24,910
Especially because the subways looked like
this.

10
00:00:24,910 --> 00:00:26,470
Which makes my daily commute to Manhattan

11
00:00:26,470 --> 00:00:28,820
