85
00:03:39,389 --> 00:03:41,699
that none of the guys circled in those photos

86
00:03:41,699 --> 00:03:43,909
are even American.

87
00:03:43,909 --> 00:03:46,540
So the CIA isn’t part of the foreign forces,

88
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:48,489
